data.description: Welcome to your dream home with an incredible low 2.75% ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE RATE OFFER! You’ll love this 4BR / 2.5BA Colonial nestled in the highly sought-after High Point community. This home offers an opportunity for an assumable VA mortgage with a low 2.75% rate. Veterans and non-veterans are eligible. The current balance of $248,000 is assumable with the remaining in down payment (or financed separately). Lower monthly payments and long-term savings make this unbeatable in today's market. Here’s a few of the home’s highlights: Welcoming 2-story foyer with beautiful wood flooring. Spacious Living, Dining, and Office spaces. Gourmet Kitchen with ample counter space, cabinets, and stainless appliances (all included). Family Room with a wood-burning fireplace and access to an extra-large wood deck. First-floor laundry with Washer, Dryer, & additional Fridge (included). Master BR featuring vaulted ceilings and an ensuite bath with a stunning walk-in tile shower. Three additional bedrooms with shared main bath complete the second floor. Large walkout basement with a pool table (included). Picturesque backyard on over 1/4 acre, featuring an outdoor concrete patio accessible from the walkout basement. This home is situated in a prime location offering easy access to private neighborhood amenities, including a pool, tennis courts, playground, basketball courts, and clubhouse. Furnace/AC (2017). Roof (2011). America’s Preferred One Year home warranty. Outdoor trampoline can stay.
